text: Sabrina Fredrica Washington (born 27 October 1978) is a British singer. She writes songs and dances, and is also businesswoman and TV personality. She was a member of the female garage/hip hop band Mis-Teeq. Category:English R&B; singers Category:Singer-songwriters from London Category:Hip hop singers Category:Living people Category:1978 births
title: Sabrina Washington
